'''什洛莫·本哈伊姆'''（Shlomo Ben-Haim，{{bd|1957年|10月15日||}}），出生于[[以色列|以色列]]，医学博士、理学博士，专攻医疗保健与生物科技领域的医学教授、创业家、慈善家。他是 Biosense Inc.、Spectrum Dynamics Medical Inc.、<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.spectrum-dynamics.com/about/board_of_directors.html|title=PhotoMedex Inc (PHMD.O)|accessdate=2015-03-09|work=|publisher=Reuters|archive-date=2016-03-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303191439/http://www.spectrum-dynamics.com/about/board_of_directors.html|dead-url=no}}</ref> MetaCure Inc.、Influence Inc.、Radiancy Inc.、X-Technologies、Impulse Dynamics N.V.、InStent Inc.和 Disc-O-Tech Ltd.等公司的共同创办人。他拥有约 480 项专利和专利申请。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://worldwide.espacenet.com/searchResults?compact=false&ST=advanced&IN=Shlomo+Ben+Haim&locale=en_EP&DB=EPODOC|title=Patent Search|accessdate=2015-03-09|work=|publisher=Espacenet}}</ref> 他也曾是 Spectrum Dynamics Medical, Inc. 公司GP/肿瘤医学顾问委员会的成员。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bloomberg.com/research/stocks/private/person.asp?personId=972824&privcapId=27512486&previousCapId=737185&previousTitle=Biosense%2520Webster%2520%2528Israel%2529%2520Ltd.|title=Shlomo A. Ben-Haim M.D.|accessdate=2015-03-09|work=|publisher=Bloomberg Business|archive-date=2015-04-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150402183311/http://www.bloomberg.com/research/stocks/private/person.asp?personId=972824&privcapId=27512486&previousCapId=737185&previousTitle=Biosense%2520Webster%2520%2528Israel%2529%2520Ltd.|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==教育背景==

本哈伊姆拥有[[以色列理工学院|以色列理工学院]]医学院的医学博士学位，以色列理工学院生理学与生物物理学系以及生物医学工程系的理学博士学位。他曾接受过以下方面的教育：核子物理、数学、生物医学工程、哲学以及医学。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.spectrum-dynamics.com/about/board_of_directors.html|title=About Spectrum|accessdate=2015-03-09|work=|publisher=Spectrum Dynamics Medical|archive-date=2016-03-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303191439/http://www.spectrum-dynamics.com/about/board_of_directors.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==学术职位==
本哈伊姆在[[哈佛大学|哈佛大学]]和以色列理工学院担任过医学、生理学和生物物理学教授。他在同行评审期刊上发表了 300 多篇科技论文。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://scholar.google.com/scholar?q=author%3A%22s+ben+haim%22&btnG=&hl=en&as_sdt=1%2C5|title=A Novel Method for Nonfluoroscopic Catheter-based Electroanatomical Mapping of the Heart|accessdate=2015-03-09|work=|publisher=Google}}</ref>他曾是强生下属公司 Biosense-Webster 的首席科学家。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.milkeninstitute.org/events/conferences/global-conference/2008/speaker-detail/3061|title=Shlomo Ben-Haim|accessdate=2015-03-09|work=|publisher=Milken Institute|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141103100135/http://www.milkeninstitute.org/events/conferences/global-conference/2008/speaker-detail/3061|archive-date=2014-11-03|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

==创业==
本哈伊姆主要在医疗保健和生物科技领域创办、共同创办或管理了大量的企业。1993 年，他共同创办了 Biosense（后来与 Webster 合并，成为强生下属公司 Biosense-Webster Inc.）。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.globes.co.il/en/article-1000810965|title=Israel attracts global healthcare giant|accessdate=2015-03-10|work=|publisher=Globes|archive-date=2014-11-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141103094325/http://www.globes.co.il/en/article-1000810965|dead-url=no}}</ref>1996 年，<ref name="#1">{{cite web|url=http://www.haaretz.com/print-edition/business/johnson-johnson-invests-80m-in-impulse-dynamics-1.158556|title=Johnson & Johnson invests $80m in Impulse Dynamics|accessdate=2015-03-10|work=|publisher=Ha'Aretz|archive-date=2016-08-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160809014953/http://www.haaretz.com/print-edition/business/johnson-johnson-invests-80m-in-impulse-dynamics-1.158556|dead-url=no}}</ref>他创办了 Impulse Dynamics公司，并担任董事长。2000 年，他参与了 Impulse Dynamics、<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.thefreelibrary.com/Guidant+and+Johnson+%26+Johnson+Announce+Comprehensive+Technology...-a061229590|title=Guidant and Johnson & Johnson Announce Comprehensive Technology Agreement; Guidant Acquires Exclusive Option to Impulse Dynamics Heart Failure Technology.|accessdate=2015-03-10|work=|publisher=The Free Library by Farlex|archive-date=2018-07-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180703133920/https://www.thefreelibrary.com/Guidant+and+Johnson+%26+Johnson+Announce+Comprehensive+Technology...-a061229590|dead-url=no}}</ref>Guidant<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.haaretz.com/print-edition/business/professor-with-a-midas-touch-1.125098|title=Professor with a Midas touch|accessdate=2015-03-10|work=|publisher=Ha'Aretz|archive-date=2017-05-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170515080709/http://www.haaretz.com/print-edition/business/professor-with-a-midas-touch-1.125098|dead-url=no}}</ref>、强生之间的三方交易。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://articles.latimes.com/2000/apr/05/business/fi-16072|title=J&J Strikes Heart Device Deal With Guidant|accessdate=2015-03-10|work=|publisher=Los Angeles Times|archive-date=2014-12-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141219140642/http://articles.latimes.com/2000/apr/05/business/fi-16072|dead-url=no}}</ref>2003 年，他创办了 MetaCure Inc.公司，<ref name="#2">{{cite web|url=http://www.bloomberg.com/research/stocks/private/person.asp?personId=972824&privcapId=27512486&previousCapId=737185&previousTitle=Biosense%2520Webster%2520%2528Israel%2529%2520Ltd.|title=Shlomo A. Ben-Haim M.D.|accessdate=2015-03-10|work=|publisher=Bloomberg Business|archive-date=2015-04-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150402183311/http://www.bloomberg.com/research/stocks/private/person.asp?personId=972824&privcapId=27512486&previousCapId=737185&previousTitle=Biosense%2520Webster%2520%2528Israel%2529%2520Ltd.|dead-url=no}}</ref>并担任董事长。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.metacure.com/about-us-2/board-of-directors/|title=Board of Directors|accessdate=2015-03-10|work=|publisher=Metacure|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150228012600/http://www.metacure.com/about-us-2/board-of-directors/|archivedate=2015-02-28}}</ref>2005年，他共同创办了 Spectrum Dynamics Inc.。公司心脏方面的业务后来与柏盛国际有限公司合并，并与后者在非心脏方面的应用成立了一家合资公司。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.globes.co.il/en/article-1000846216|title=Biosensors buys Spectrum Dynamics|accessdate=2015-03-10|work=|publisher=Globes|archive-date=2014-11-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141103094332/http://www.globes.co.il/en/article-1000846216|dead-url=no}}</ref>

本哈伊姆博士也在心脏病学、肥胖症、糖尿病、美容与化妆品、抗病毒药物治疗、深静脉血栓预防、肢体缺血治疗、中风后遗症与运动损伤康复等领域，共同创办了多种其他的医疗设备及生物医学公司。<ref name="#2"/>
2005 年，美国医疗保健公司强生宣布投资 8 千万美元到 Impulse Dynamics公司——，即本哈伊姆与美国企业家 Lewis Pell 于 1996 年共同创办的一家公司。该项投资发生在2004 年，但是一年以后才予以宣布。<ref name="#1"/>

迄今为止，本哈伊姆在医疗保健行业共同创办的其他公司有：已合并到 Medtronic 的InStent Inc.公司，已合并到 Kyphon的 Disc-O-Tech Ltd.公司， Kyphon 之后合并到 Medtronic公司，之后合并到 Photomedex 的 Radiancy Inc.公司，之后合并到 Guidant 的 X-Technologies公司，Impulse Dynamics N.V.公司和Influence Inc.公司。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://gojisolutions.com/Company.aspx?p=2|title=Executive Team|accessdate=2015-03-10|work=|publisher=Goji|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141105075713/http://gojisolutions.com/Company.aspx?p=2|archivedate=2014-11-05}}</ref>本哈伊姆还共同创办了 Goji，现在担任 Goji 的董事长，Goji 正在开发创新能源输送技术。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.gojisolutions.com/|title=Executive Team|accessdate=2015-03-10|work=|publisher=Goji|archive-date=2017-08-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170811001601/http://www.gojisolutions.com/|dead-url=no}}</ref>本哈伊姆教授共同创办了数家公司，之后以超过 10 亿美元的金额出售或合并，其中包括了以下公司的出售：Biosense 出售给强生，Influence 出售给 AMS， 以及 X-Technologies 出售给 Guidant。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.hobart-group.com|title=About Hobart|accessdate=2015-03-09|work=|publisher=Hobart Group|archive-date=2020-12-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201205112742/https://hobart-group.com/|dead-url=no}}</ref>更详细的信息见下表：
