==奖项和奖励==
本哈伊姆因其研究与发明获得过多项奖项。所获奖项包括：居鲁丹生物医学研究奖，有名的安德里亚·格朗兹格最佳发明家奖。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bloomberg.com/research/stocks/private/person.asp?personId=972824&privcapId=27512486&previousCapId=737185&previousTitle=Biosense%2520Webster%2520%2528Israel%2529%2520Ltd.|title=Shlomo Ben-Haim|accessdate=2015-03-09|work=|publisher=Bloomberg Business|archive-date=2015-04-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150402183311/http://www.bloomberg.com/research/stocks/private/person.asp?personId=972824&privcapId=27512486&previousCapId=737185&previousTitle=Biosense%2520Webster%2520%2528Israel%2529%2520Ltd.|dead-url=no}}</ref>
2012 年，本哈伊姆获得爱荷华医学校友会授予的内科医学奖。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.healthcare.uiowa.edu/alumni/awards/previous.html|title=Past Alumni Award Recipients|accessdate=2015-03-09|work=|publisher=Medicine Alumni Society|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141103100857/http://www.healthcare.uiowa.edu/alumni/awards/previous.html|archivedate=2014-11-03}}</ref>2014 年 9 月 17 日，哈佛医学院的教学医院（贝斯以色列女执事医疗中心，BIDMC）评价他为“一位在国际上享有盛誉的心脏病学家，他开发了多种纠正人类心脏电气系统中存在的致命问题的新方法。”<ref>{{cite web|url=http://hms.harvard.edu/news/ben-haim-professorship-established-cardiac-electrophysiology|title=Ben-Haim Professorship Established in Cardiac Electrophysiology|accessdate=2015-03-09|work=|publisher=Harvard Medical School|archive-date=2017-08-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170805125000/https://hms.harvard.edu/news/ben-haim-professorship-established-cardiac-electrophysiology|dead-url=no}}</ref>在哈佛医学院举行的一次宴会上，推出了“ 为纪念Mark E. Josephson 的心脏电生理学领域的什洛莫·本哈伊姆医学博士医学教授职位”。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bidmc.org/News/Around-BIDMC/2014/September/JosephsonChair.aspx|title=BIDMC Celebrates Career of Cardiac Electrophysiology Pioneer with Professorship|accessdate=2015-03-09|work=|publisher=Beth Israel Deaconess Medical Center|archive-date=2016-03-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303221358/http://www.bidmc.org/News/Around-BIDMC/2014/September/JosephsonChair.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref>据说本哈伊姆用他的“慷慨大礼”使之“成为可能”。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.milkeninstitute.org/events/conferences/global-conference/2008/speaker-detail/3061/about/board_of_directors.html|title=Shlomo Ben-Haim|accessdate=2015-03-09|work=|publisher=Milken Institute}}{{dead link|date=2017年11月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>

==社会责任==
本哈伊姆积极参与各种社会项目。他成立了一个慈善基金会，寻求改善那些在贫困社区的人的健康与教育。[https://web.archive.org/web/20141103100135/http://www.milkeninstitute.org/events/conferences/global-conference/2008/speaker-detail/3061]2008 年，他与荷兰社会投资基金 George Avenue 一同发起了 Al Bawader 基金，将混合回报投资瞄准在以色列-阿拉伯的商业社区中。该基金旨在为以色列-阿拉伯学者创造就业机会，同时为以色列-阿拉伯的企业建立一个高科技行业。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.assifero.org/oggetti/1409.pdf/about/board_of_directors.html|title=Letter from the Chair|accessdate=2015-03-09|work=|publisher=EVPA}}{{dead link|date=2017年11月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>

